Package bankmanager

Provides the classes necessary to handle user and atm requests that require high-level authorization.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AccountManager
    Account Manager handles all requests relating to Account delegated from Bank Manager.
    BankManager
    The Bank Manager class can fulfill requests submitted through the ATM that the ATM cannot perform by either doing them or delegating them to one of 3 other responsible managers: AccountManager, TransactionManager, and UserManager.
    TransactionManager
    The Transaction Manager handles all requests related to Transaction as delegated by the BankManager.
    UserManager
    The User Manager handles all requests related to User delegated from BankManager.

Package bankmanager Description

Provides the classes necessary to handle user and atm requests that require high-level authorization.

Bank Manager is the parent class of the other classes in the package. Each child class is responsible for handling a set of related specific requests.
